FuncDef: This command specifies how many ISAs may be in active use by the WLAN-GW group at the same time. If the maximum number of active ISAs is reached and more ISAs are added to the group, the new ISAs are considered to be in standby mode.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the number of WLAN-GW ISAs intended for active use. Values-1 to 14.
